      "content": "i know the inr thing but i literally can't get an appointment for weeks and i'm just not comfortable staying on 5mg if i don't need it. if i just do 3mg for a week then drop to 2mg, basically just listening to my body, would that typically be okay? like is there any reason why a lower dose would actually be bad for someone who is already super healthy and active?",
